<dialog id="raid-spreadsheet-intro"
        class="dfe-f-modal govuk-!-margin-0"
        data-module="dfe-f-modal"
        data-raid-ss-intro="true"
        data-storage-key="compass.raid.spreadsheet-intro"
        aria-labelledby="raid-spreadsheet-intro-title"
        aria-describedby="raid-spreadsheet-intro-desc"
        aria-modal="true"
        role="dialog">
  <div class="dfe-f-modal__panel">
    <header class="dfe-f-modal__header">
      <h2 id="raid-spreadsheet-intro-title" class="govuk-heading-m dfe-f-modal__title">Using the RAID spreadsheet</h2>
      <button type="button" class="dfe-f-modal__close" data-dfe-modal-close data-raid-ss-intro-dismiss aria-label="Close">
        <span class="dfe-f-modal__close-x" aria-hidden="true">×</span>
      </button>
    </header>
    <div class="dfe-f-modal__body" id="raid-spreadsheet-intro-desc">
      <p class="govuk-body">Manage risks and issues in a spreadsheet-style table. You can customise the layout and filter rows.</p>
      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li><strong>Expand table</strong> — view the table full screen, like a spreadsheet.</li>
        <li><strong>Filters</strong> (funnel icon) — show filter controls under every column. Use dropdowns for status, dates, scores, and similar fields. Type in the search boxes on ref, title, description, and other text columns to filter by partial text.</li>
        <li><strong>Reorder columns</strong> (left–right arrows) — turn on reorder mode, then drag a column header. Use the keyboard icon if you cannot use drag and drop.</li>
        <li><strong>Column width</strong> — drag the line on the right edge of a header to resize. With a header focused, use <kbd>Alt</kbd> + <kbd>←</kbd> / <kbd>→</kbd> to narrow or widen.</li>
        <li><strong>Wrap text</strong> — toggle whether long text in title, description, and similar columns wraps or is truncated.</li>
        <li><strong>Zoom in / Zoom out</strong> — change the table size. <strong>Reset table</strong> (circular arrow) asks you to confirm before restoring default zoom, column widths, and order.</li>
        <li><strong>Show guide</strong> (info icon) — opens this help again.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="govuk-body-s govuk-!-margin-bottom-0" style="color:#505a5f;">This guide is shown once until you dismiss it. Use <strong>Show guide</strong> in the toolbar to open it again.</p>
    </div>
    <footer class="dfe-f-modal__footer">
      <button type="button" class="govuk-button" data-module="govuk-button" data-raid-ss-intro-dismiss>Got it</button>
    </footer>
  </div>
</dialog>
